{"tid":2106781,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"黃碧雲一事睇得出泛民本性難移：唔受歡迎即割","createTime":"2020-07-13T13:24:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-13T14:28:10.000Z","uid":63822,"like":18,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"c36bbf60e92350f96638fbf799a99df62eb8a969","tid":2106781,"uid":63822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T13:24:25.000Z","msg":"黃碧雲完全四面楚歌<br />\n<br />\n然而成個泛民，包括佢既黨友都冇咩邊個出嚟幫佢講好說話<br />\n<br />\n一失勢即割，唔好拖我落水，我要保住自己果席<br />\n<br />\n我地一直都誤會左，泛民14年原來並唔係割勇武，割人衝<br />\n<br />\n而係唔理你係咩立場，咩理念，只要你唔受歡迎就割<br />\n<br />\n同你合作有機會令自己選票減少就割，無論你既動機同目的係乜<br />\n<br />\n今次初選捉蟲入屎忽，即刻割黃碧雲，同黨其他候選人好似互不相識咁，其實都幾撚慘<br />\n<br />\n選舉真係照妖鏡"},{"pid":"1ddbb03a19541314e0d6c017e1e5a9b1b99a777b","tid":2106781,"uid":26770,"like":23,"dislike":3,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T13:25:43.000Z","msg":"若飯民護黃碧雲你又會話護短"},{"pid":"97c853381db497e86c8d1af61d3633b94dc5c23a","tid":2106781,"uid":173814,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T13:26:11.000Z","msg":"失民意就梗係割<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ee2f87ac60fccee29b1f1e28c87391082bf7bc4","tid":2106781,"uid":177089,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T13:28:49.000Z","msg":"泛民先係民主進程毒瘤"},{"pid":"5023dfb42b7ff9ad8947a6636efeff7c08bb9a41","tid":2106781,"uid":135040,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"1ddbb03a19541314e0d6c017e1e5a9b1b99a777b","tid":2106781,"uid":26770,"like":23,"dislike":3,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T13:25:43.000Z","msg":"若飯民護黃碧雲你又會話護短"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T13:30:46.000Z","msg":"做乜都錯，死棋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7412e2e4e5e7e0e2c54b5087465eb9e1cbedea7","tid":2106781,"uid":107790,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T13:34:08.000Z","msg":"係割應該一早割<br />\n一係比新人上<br />\n一係廢涂返九西 超區換人"},{"pid":"ca15a3c1837c66b844edfc190cb83993d104a19e","tid":2106781,"uid":71253,"like":1,"d